governance is an question open for public discussion.

## hive proposals

proposals can be submitted to hives.

### parties involved

all members of the hive

### process involved

spectrum of possibilities
- consensus only, everyone must agree
- all but n consensus
- percent agreement
- supermajority in favor
- majority in favor
- largest minority

## hive bank

the hive must keep inventory of its financial resources.

### parties involved

the treasurer(s)

### error checking

all members of the hive can submit proposals as a form of bug reporting
